# Data Table Rules

## Table Style

- Use abp-table or DataTables
- Enable:
  - hoverable rows
  - striped rows

## Columns

- First column: thumbnail or icon
- Main column: title (bold)
- Secondary: category / date
- Status: badge
- Last column: actions (icon buttons)

## Actions

- Edit (icon)
- Delete (icon)
- No text buttons

## UX

- Add search input on top
- Add filters:
  - category
  - status

- Pagination bottom right

## Empty State

- Show:
  "No data available"
  + button create